Description: # py-msyh
        python utils to use font msyh.ttf in a minute.
        
        # install
        `pip install py-msyh`
        
        # usage
        ```python
        import pymsyh
        # get font path of msyh.ttf
        font_path=pymsyh.get_font_path()
        # load font (using ImageFont.truetype from PIL)
        font= pymsyh.load_font(size=24)
        ```
